ngs===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"4\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Official New Zealand Music Chart|NZ<br />Hot]]<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/hotsingles?chart=4543|title=NZ Hot Singles Chart|publisher=Recorded Music NZ|date=22 October 2018|accessdate=19 October 2018}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Bubbling Under Hot 100|US<br />Bub.]]<br /><ref name=\"Bubbling\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs|US<br />R&B<br />/HH<br />Bub.]]<br /><ref name=\"Bubbling R&B\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Hot R&B Songs|US<br />R&B]]<br /><ref name=\"US R&B Songs\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Good Bad\"\n| rowspan=\"4\"| 2018\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 18\n| rowspan=\"4\"| ''Ella Mai''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Sauce\"\n| 20 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 23\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Everything\"<br />{{small|(featuring [[John Legend]])}}\n| 23 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 14\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Gut Feeling\"<br />{{small|(featuring [[H.E.R.]])}}\n| 31 || 21 || 9 || 11\n|-\n| colspan=\"12\" style=\"font-size:85%\"| \"\u2014\" denotes a recording that did not chart\n|}\n\n====Notes====\n{{notelist-ua}}\n\n===Guest appearances===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! scope=\"col\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\"| Other artist(s)\n! scope=\"col\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"10,000 Hours\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/10-000-hours-feat-ella-mai/1160481897|title=Cold Summer by DJ Mustard on Apple Music|work=iTunes Store|accessdate=9 October 2018}}</ref>\n| 2016\n| [[DJ Mustard]]\n| ''[[Cold Summer (DJ Mustard album)|Cold Summer]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Hit Me Up\"<r